The paper involves game theory and machine learning, which are both topics that fall under the category of theoretical computer science (cs.TC). However, the specific focus on data acquisition games and the analysis of equilibria suggest that the paper is more likely to be categorized under game theory (cs.GT) or machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of machine learning models and the consideration of the welfare of consumers suggest that the paper could also be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the analysis of the action space and the consideration of pricing suggest that the paper could also be categorized under information theory (cs.IT).
